headline: Should You Reassess T. Rowe Price After Shares Climb 1.4% This Month?
summary: Thinking about what to do with T. Rowe Price Group stock? You are not alone. After a rocky few years, the shares are showing some signs of renewed momentum, but a deeper look is needed before making a move. The stock closed at $104.96 most recently, marking a modest 0.7% gain for the week and a 1.4% climb over the past month. headline: Resilience Announces Long-Term Financing of up to $825 Million to Accelerate CDMO Strategy
summary: CINCINNATI, October 29, 2025--National Resilience ("Resilience"), a technology-focused biomanufacturing company dedicated to broadening access to complex medicines, today announced long-term debt financing of up to $825 million from Oak Hill Advisors ("OHA") to strengthen its balance sheet and fuel its growth plans. This new capital will enable Resilience to accelerate its CDMO business strategy and invest in its go-forward manufacturing operations anchored in Cincinnati and Toronto.
